<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Arn says Magister tries to operate in areas where they wont run into other guilds/groups. He says he doesnt care to please anyone but himself. I think we can assume that his game play can be classified as anti social by these examples.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
