Da`kor: always among the first to smash something.  Usually with lower numbers than the other guys.  You see the Da`kor guildtag, you know the person is pretty damn good at playing their class. At their peak Da`kor was a pretty close knit group of people who had been together for the most part for a good while. A lot of the people in Magister, I've never heard of(not that thats a deciding factor, but hell, I know or at least have heard of damn near everybody on the server in the 57+ crowd).<br>
